# Summary
This documentation explains three methods for creating cohorts in Amplitude: using Microscope to create static or behavioral cohorts from chart data points, importing cohorts from CSV files containing user/group IDs, and creating inline behavioral or interval cohorts directly within the Segmentation module of most chart types.

